
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-zeng-nvo3-l3-vm-migration-00.txt'>
    <title>"Layer 3 Cross-site VM Live Migration Scheme", Lieguang Zeng, Xu Yang, Mao Yang, Yong Li, Depeng Jin, Li Su</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-zeng-nvo3-l3-vm-migration-00.txt</link>
    <description>This document utilizes software-defined network (SDN) to propose a cross-site live VM migration scheme in layer 3 environment. The architecture and main components are described in detail. The components include central controller, local controller, gateway and virtual switch, which are in charge of cross-site communication management, in-site network configuration, inter-site connection and VM address resolution respectively. This scheme can implement layer 3 cross-site VM migration without using complex mechanism.</description>
    <dc:date>2014-06-12T07:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
